item.title: Hi, I'm Austin.
item.description: TEST Nice to finally meet you, it’s been too long. First, thank you for taking the time to read some of the things I’ve written. Second, here are a few things about me. I’m a biochemist turned computer nerd from the great urban fold of Denver, CO.
